{"tid":1626724,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)高草魅聲 恐怖遊輪 死神凶盒 沽注一擲(雷曼事件)","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:45:54.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c385ac71ed60c4c6db790d744f7d1d3018ed436a","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=e711195f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=712e54c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=1c154f5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.dramaqueen.com.tw/images/video_poster/2019/201909161712362825ce6e4f5de112a0183db5288e59065551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dramaqueen.com.tw%2Fimages%2Fvideo_poster%2F2019%2F201909161712362825ce6e4f5de112a0183db5288e59065551.jpg&h=2723fed0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b4/Triangle_(Christopher_Smith).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb4%2FTriangle_%28Christopher_Smith%29.jpg&h=87a097be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://assets.wmoov.com/movie/photo/201708/p2460025207_1504187002.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wmoov.com%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201708%2Fp2460025207_1504187002.jpg&h=2037d045&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/be/The_Big_Short_2015_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fbe%2FThe_Big_Short_2015_Poster.jpg&h=6d1939d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名懷孕的女子和她哥哥聽到一位男孩的求救聲，兩人隨即踏進一片廣大的高草地中，卻發現可能再也走出不來了。<br />\n<br />\n2.潔西（梅麗莎&middot;喬治飾）是一個單身母親，有一個患有自閉症的兒子湯米。她的朋友格雷格（麥可&middot;多爾曼飾）邀請她周末一起乘「三角洲號」遊艇出海遊玩，同行的還有海瑟（艾瑪&middot;朗飾）、薩莉（雷切爾&middot;卡爾帕尼飾）、唐尼（亨利&middot;尼克森飾）、維克多（利亞姆&middot;海莫斯沃斯飾）。出海不久，潔西內心始終籠罩著一股不祥預感，正當大夥沉浸在歡樂的派對氣氛時，埋伏潔西腦海的擔憂竟然成真&hellip;原本萬里無雲的好天氣驟轉成狂風暴雨，遊艇也在驚滔駭浪的摧殘下翻覆。遇難的眾人只好登上一艘航行經過的郵輪尋求協助。但是，登船後，潔西卻對郵輪上的一切感到似曾相識，一行人也開始接二連三地目睹地獄般的殘虐景象，甚至遭遇蒙面殺人狂的追殺，一連串超乎常理的神祕事件，逐步將眾人推往萬劫不復的恐怖輪迴中&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.高中生嘉兒（祖兒京治 飾）一直活喺媽媽自殺嘅陰影之下，喺學校又遭受欺凌，生活十分不順。有日佢偶爾發現，爸爸（賴恩菲臘 飾）從垃圾堆中執返嚟嘅音樂盒可以幫佢實現7個願望，於是半信半疑嘅佢對住盒子許願。點知願望竟然一一成真，金錢、人緣、愛情&hellip;&hellip;要乜有乜<br />\n<br />\n4.故事改編自真人真事，敘述在2007年&ndash;2008年環球金融危機期間，四位以專業手法操作著金融業而進行大賣空、就此獲利的驚人事蹟<br />\n<br />\n9 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=02c05453\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrk1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=b4f92eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910861e424b2f5d9a133cc984828dd046c304adb","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17fcd4b7fda68f12514056483c0b3254a8b64ea","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a85bb928ec66c712f40bd3f5accd48bfdb40d91","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db30b0244fe96eeadd66338f75393dc6a078cee3","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b893af97d6c7a6b9d8c8a4cd1f8595c90b0a609","tid":1626724,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}